

Liberty Prime is a giant robot from the Fallout video game series. He was created by the United States government to help in the fight against the communists during the Cold War. However, Liberty Prime was never completed and was eventually abandoned in the ruins of Boston.

In Fallout 3, Liberty Prime is discovered by the Brotherhood of Steel and is brought back to working order. He is then sent to help the Brotherhood in their fight against the Enclave.

In Fallout 4, Liberty Prime is again discovered by the Brotherhood of Steel. This time, he is sent to help the player character in their fight against the Institute.
